PrecisAmendment to the AIR REGULATIONS expanding the definition of "critical surfaces" to include the upper fuselage on aircraft with rear mounted engines, allowing frost, on the underside of the wings, in certain limited circumstances and allowing operators to comply with the regulation by use of a ground icing operations program.
